 Lingua::PT::Abbrev version 0.05
=================================

An abbreviations dictionary manager for NLP


ABSTRACT

This module handles a built-in abbreviations dictionary, and a user
customized abbreviations dictionary. It provides handy functions for
NLP processing.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


